details.responsibilities:
- Reporting to Branch Manager, you will be responsible for soliciting new banking accounts acquisition and activation, from sources identified and assigned by the Bank, and generate referrals for other green products to relevant business units.
- Job Responsibilities:
- Meet and exceed activities target assigned;
- Conduct proactive outbound calls from customer leads and invite customers to open new bank accounts which include, but not limit to, securities/investment account, VIP Banking, YOU Banking;
- Ensure activation of securities/investment accounts by inviting customers to perform the first investment transction;
- Passing successfully activated accounts to Sky RM units for further relationship management;
- Cross-sell other green products as directed by the Bank from time to time and create sales referrals to branch colleagues or other departments as appropriate;
- Maintain accurate record keeping using prevailing branch systems;
- Uphold Bank branding and image by conducting tasks professionally and interact with customers courteously;
- Handle customer enquiries and provide relevant services within own capacity.  Refer the enquiries duly to relevant parties should it be beyond own capacity;
- Participate in localized or off-site promotional activities
